貫.definition: to pierce through; to pass through; to be stringed together; string of 1000 cash

貫串.definition: to pierce through; to string together

貫徹.definition: to implement; to put into practice; to carry out

貫徹始終.definition: to follow through; to carry through to the end

貫氣.definition: (feng shui) beneficial influence, esp. from one's ancestral graves; to confer a beneficial influence

貫通.definition: to link up; to thread together

貫連.definition: to link up; to join together; to connect
